        }
        .header {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .content {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .content p {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-style: italic;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <p class="header">Dear {!Lead.Name},</p>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>This is a gentle reminder about your scheduled site visit to Epitome Integrated City on <strong></strong> at <strong>[Time]</strong>. We are looking forward to welcoming you and showing you our projects and facilities.</p>

            <p>If you have any questions or need further assistance before the visit, please do not hesitate to reach out to us.</p>
